Package base_SOM_Objects.som_examples.base

Class baseDataPtVis

java.lang.Object
base_SOM_Objects.som_examples.base.baseDataPtVis
Direct Known Subclasses:
SOM_Example
public abstract class baseDataPtVis extends Object
This class holds functionality for rendering on the map. Since this functionality is fundamentally different than the necessary functionality for feature calculation/manipulation we have it separate from the base example class
